Menopause
[[Image:Ovary.jpg|thumb|The cause of most women bitchiness]]

Menopause is what happens when women become absolutely useless. The woman with such an affliction will come to realize this, and so become more of a [[bitch]] than ever before. By this time the [[woman]] has become very [[old]], her breasts will sag (more), she'll gain (more) wrinkles, she'll have become ugly(er), and she will have "accidents" outside of the bathroom (more often). Thus her bitchiness will be no excuse any longer, as the respectable [[man]] will realize that he will never get laid by her again (and indeed, will no longer want to), as opposed to the .000000000001% chance of having sex with his wife he had before the menopause. This will cause him to walk out on her, which only justifies her fears and makes her symptoms worse. With combined irritability, hot flashes (which are not as "hot" as one would think), weight gain, and gassiness, [[you]] will be lucky enough to make it out alive, especially if this lady is [[your mom]].



==Pre-Menopause, "The Good Years"==

Or, as should it be, the semi-unpainful years. Women are bitchy at this stage but it's offset by the fact that they are sometimes willing to [[fuck]]. Some lucky girls aren't even that [[fat]] and thus the [[pimp|respectable man]] will not even have to close his eyes when receiving the blowjob. It should be noted that wimminz at this stage do not have much cooking experience, therefore the [[sammich]]es will not be the most tasty. Nevertheless, she will learn quickly with a good backhand or ten.

==Menopause==
At this stage (around 60 or so), an average woman will have hit menopause. This means that her ovaries are beginning to stop working and her hormones are running more rampant that a twelve year old girl who just hit [[puberty]]. Since women are only good for:

*Birthing sons
*Sex
*Making sandwiches

and she can no longer do two out of the three (since it is doubtful she will be able to get wet with her uterus all dried up), she will begin to feel useless. This is magnified as her hormones hold her hostage, making her flip from "happy" to "bitch" to "FLAMING ANTI-CHRIST FROM HELL WHO HAS COME TO DEVOUR YOUR SOUL".

